{
  "id": "adv_card_ai_04_02",
  "title": "小美山愛 2話 全軍突撃！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "―― the next day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1066.6666667,
          "startTime": 1.0666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "失礼します！　教官殿！\nお時間をいただいてもよろしいでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Excuse me! Commander!\nMay I take a moment of your time?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "教官じゃない。マネージャーだ\n何かあったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not an commander. I'm a manager.\nWhat's going on?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "はっ！　自分、例の指令について困っておりまして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ha!　I'm having trouble with the order.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "口調は普通でいいから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just keep your tone normal.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい、分かりました\nこれなんですけど、困ってて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ha‚ yes‚ I understand.\nI'm having trouble with this ……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "これは……昨日、資料として渡したゲームじゃないか\n何が分からないんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Isn't this the game info you got …… yesterday as a resource?\nWhat don't you understand?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "あの、いくらプロモーションとはいえ、私のプレイが\nへっぽこ過ぎたら、みなさん、興ざめだと思うんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I think people would be disappointed if I play too poorly‚\nno matter if it's just a promo or not.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "私が上手にプレイ出来た方が\nイベントも盛り上がるんじゃないでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wouldn't the event be more exciting\nif I could play it well?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "まあ確かにその通りだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ you're certainly right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "それに、ゲームの魅力をちゃんと伝えるには\nゲームの魅力を理解していないとダメだと思うんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ I think you have to understand the game's appeal\nin order to properly convey the game's appeal.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "愛の言う通りだ。愛自身がこのゲームを好きになれば\nその気持ちは、お客さんにきっと伝わるはずだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai is right‚ if Ai loves this game‚\nher feeling will surely be conveyed to the audience.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "ですよね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I knew it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。愛の腹筋に、ゲーム愛が加われば\n必ずイベントは成功する",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. If Ai's abs plus the love for the game‚\nthe event will surely be a success!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "ふ、腹筋のことは言わないで下さい！\n恥ずかしいですから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh‚ don't mention the abs!\nIt's embarrassing. ……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、ごめん。……で、何が分からないんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ sorry. What is it about …… that you don't understand?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "はい、だからゲームをやってみようと思ったんですけど\nどうやったら、私のスマホで遊べるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ so I thought I would try the game‚\nbut how can I play it on my phone?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……これはパソコンがないと遊べないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…… You'll need a computer to play this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？　パソコンって\nお仕事と動画を観る以外にも使えるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What?　Can you use a computer\nfor something other than working and watching videos?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "小美山二等兵、そこからなのか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Private Komiyama‚ you need a special training…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.8666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5266.666666600003,
          "startTime": 110.1333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5266.666666600003,
          "startTime": 110.1333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.9
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "どうしてゲームセンターに来たんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What brought you to the game station?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "愛のプロモーションするゲームは元々\nアーケードで人気があったものを移植した作品なんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The games Ai promotes are ports of games\nthat were originally popular in arcades.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "あーけーど？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Arcades?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "……ごめん、アーケードゲームって言われても\n分からないよな。要は業務用ってことだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…… Sorry‚ so you don't know what is an arcade game.\nThe point is that we need to promo this game.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "愛はパソコンを持ってないだろう？\nそれならここでプレイした方が手っ取り早い",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And Ai wouldn't have a computer‚ right?\nThen it's quicker to play it here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど！　では、早速プレイしてみますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see!　Well‚ I'll play it right away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.6,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gun-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6756.66669040001,
          "startTime": 142.3566666904
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 141.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02-ai014.m4a",
      "text": "きゃああああああっ！　当たりません！\nいくら撃っても全然当たりませんよ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aaahhh!　It won't hit!\nNo matter how much I shoot‚ I can't hit anything at all!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 148.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_02-ai015.m4a",
      "text": "敵の人が避けるから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because the enemies keep dodging!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
